casaos-docker-service (0.4.15) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Docker Compose configuration for CasaOS container (dockurr/casa:0.4.15)
  * Systemd service for container lifecycle management
  * Installs to /opt/casa with persistent data storage
  * Web UI accessible on port 80
  * Package version tracks dockurr/casa image version

